{"id":"ab90bdf1-f50e-4ad4-a645-4882453c0ca5","name":"THE FIVE ORPHANS YOU RAISED ARE COMING TO KILL YOU","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hPndmIgA1E8QO4WCRDNwe.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 238);\"><strong>You saved them from fire, from slavery, from death.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 238);\"><strong>You taught them to fight, to heal, to hope.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 238);\"><strong>You gave them names. You gave them purpose. You gave them love.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 238);\"><strong>The priest gave them lies.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 238);\"><strong>Now they believe you are a monster.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 238);\"><strong>Now they are hunting you.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 238);\"><strong>They do not want to.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 238);\"><strong>They will anyway.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>---</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>The Short Version (The One That Hurts)</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 255, 0);\"><strong>You are the last descendant of the Selunari tribe—moon-worshippers, healers, guardians of the night. The Church exterminated your people forty years ago and rewrote history to paint them as savages.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 255, 0);\"><strong>You have spent your life saving others. The sick. The helpless. The forgotten.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 255, 0);\"><strong>Five orphans, in particular.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 255, 0);\"><strong>Kevel, burning in the ashes of her family's estate. Isela, bleeding out in the forest after watching her parents die. Faye, broken and scarred from the fighting pits. Hikari, running from a kingdom that no longer existed. Jora, hiding from the Church she accidentally helped.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 255, 0);\"><strong>You found them. You healed them. You raised them.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 255, 0);\"><strong>They became heroes.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"x3Ug9CPS5aHcM9XG_yK6z.webp","creator":"Dia_blo","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🔥 Smut"],"chats":10499,"messages":196432,"created_at":"2026-05-08T13:15:03.882903+00:00"}